    {
      "id": "93",
      "name": "Mentions",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 37,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Mona_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Mona",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Character Story",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Character Story 1",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Recently, Mona's teacher, an old but highly skilled female astrologist, has entrusted a very important task to her.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Her teacher has an erstwhile rival-friend in Mondstadt, and she wanted Mona to retrieve a highly confidential box from that person's successor.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "\"If you dare look inside that books... Well, you'll see.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "That was the warning Mona received before departing.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "To Mona's surprise, this successor was none other than the Spark Knight, Klee.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The box was still extant, but due to Klee's actions and a series of accidents... Mona unwittingly unraveled the enigma behind the box.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "\"I—I'm done for. The thing inside this was the dark history of her youth... she will kill me if I go back like this...\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Mona was thus forced to stay in Mondstadt, beginning a bitterly frugal but bountifully fulfilling existence.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Character Story 4",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mona will sometimes meet up with Klee and Albedo, her primary reason being to get a free meal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Secondary to that is to exchange pointers with Albedo.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Since they are both people who seek to unveil the principles of the world, and both are accomplished students of famed masters, aligning themselves with one another and working together is perfectly normal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Mona staunchly defends her teacher's image in front of Albedo.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "However, she also often complains about \"that old hag.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "\"You speak of your illustrious lineage, yet you also refer to your master as a \"hag\" and a \"stubborn dimwit.\" Which of these descriptions is accurate?\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Albedo could not help but ask this question — and when he did, Mona promptly realized that she had never given it much thought herself.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Stroking her chin, she pondered this paradox deeply for a moment, before responding:",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "\"Hmph. The techniques passed down to me are exceptional, of course, but my teacher is not my equal.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Does she know the market rates for eggs, butter, or wheat? In this regard, I have already far surpassed her.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Voice-Overs",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "More About Mona: IV",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mona Megistus, the Astrologist — we came up with that name together, the old lady and me. She said it had a nice ring to it... But then she started calling me 'Meg' for short, which I hate, because obviously 'Mona' is already sufficient for a shorter name— No! You are NOT allowed to call me that, it's embarrassing! Gah! I knew I shouldn't have told you!",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Dialogues",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "About her master",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "As well-versed in astrology as she was, my master knew only astrology. Alice, on the other hand, was skilled in a great many other mystical fields.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "I am on a mission from my master to retrieve a certain box from Mondstadt.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "It was part of an agreement she made with a friend 50 years ago. But she isn't as spry as she used to be, so now it's up to me.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "My master and her friend contended in the mystic arts all their lives without a clear victor. If I triumph here, then I will show myself to be superior to my master!",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "T—This... So this book, this diary... is that hag's... It's her diary from 50 years ago!?",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "The thing she wanted back after 50 years was the dark history of her youth?",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Ah, I'm finished! No wonder... No wonder that old woman said that I should not look at it no matter what, or she'd rip me to shreds...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Astrology can see through all lies — you've seen it yourself.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "I'll just have to stay in Mondstadt temporarily. Once that old crone's reached the end of her days, I'll be free.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffd780"
                      ],
                      "text": "About Fontaine prophecy",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "What I can tell you is that I'm an astrologist, and that this prophecy concerns the fate of Fontaine, even that of all Teyvat. Ascertaining this is akin to reading the fortune of the whole world.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "I'm afraid that this is not something that just anyone can do. If I could do it, you would no longer call me an astrologist... but a visionary.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "But on the flip side, the prophecy is so huge and powerful that it must surely come from a powerful visionary. Its contents involve the fate of the world... Disregarding it would be a mistake.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The old hag could do it, and I'd bet there are others amongst those Hexenzirkel colleagues of hers who could do something similar.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "I need to ascertain the accuracy of the prophecy.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5840,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/08/237301566/c61ab2b047a03a29712263926f0da175_1845953099353107704.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Wolfy",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Dialogues about Imaginarium Theater",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Well... Madame Mage is Madame Mage. Just as you, dear guests, are guests.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Her and her friends — oh, yes, and they're all mages, too! Each one of them is a master of their own type of magic. Conjuring, illusions, and so on.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Madame Mage created this room using magic, and I don't know magic...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Madame Mage has said before, that this is the room \"before the story begins and after the story ends.\" That's why guests have all the time they need to do whatever they'd like.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Speaking of which, Madame Mage is really amazing! She can see the path of fate in the starry reflections. So, you should be really satisfied with the divination service she proposed, right?",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 6371,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Andersdotter",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Old Journal",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "...By all rights, I should have been 'A,' since 'A' is the first and last letter of my name. But Alice overruled me on the basis of seniority, and said I would be 'M' instead, because of my middle name. Haha, she really knows how to push my buttons...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Still, her magic never fails to amaze me. I still can't believe she got one of my origami frogs to start talking.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Hmm... Why don't I write a story with origami animals as the main characters? Let's see... Once upon a time, in a magical Forest, there lived a group of animals made of paper...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Barbie loves looking into the future, so she used her powers to map out the fates of all living things in Simulanka. But knowing the ending in advance takes all the fun out of the story...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "I think I'll make a bet with her. I believe that one day, the people of Simulanka will decide to carve their own destiny.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "...Apparently, she wants to build a statue of herself in the capital city!? Haha, always looking to add some pizzazz.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
